text: Saw a Groupon for $7 for $14 worth of food. Didn't have to print the coupon which was very convenient. My boyfriend had the 4oz Grilled Steak with steamed rice and mixed greens and I had the 4oz Grilled Chicken with brown rice and asparagus, we both enjoyed it! The guy working also was very nice and asked us how everything was, even offered some Korean BBQ sauce that came straight from Hawaii to try with our protein. Delicious. We'll definitely come back!
If it were open the last 2x I've been id give it 5 stars but since they choose when they feel like opening I'll give them 3 stars
Awesome food for the fit minded! Even offers meal prep service! Super friendly staff and accommodating to special diet needs! Must check it out! Deff going back ASAP :)
This place is absolutely delicious if I could afford to eat it everyday I would.

This place is actually really great!

At first when I drove past I didn't fully understand what exactly a "fitness cafe" was then I saw a groupon for Fix8 and I bought it so I could test it out.

Well worth it!  Entire portioned out meal for $14! and HEALTHY, I have been looking for a place like this.

Garlic steak is a must try, I will return!
